products.title: William Morris Marigold Hemp Roman Blind
products.description: With a natural eye for pattern, william morris produced designs that not only balanced figuration and order, but which were unusually distinctive for their time. Were thrilled to bring these famous designs to life as beautiful blinds in their collaboration with the v&a. products.title: William Morris Sunflower Honey Roman Blind

Part of their collaboration with the v&a, the sunflower honey roman blind is a great choice if you want to replicate a warm summer's day in your home.
